              If your vehicle is pulling to the left or to the right, then it is probably time for you to get an
              alignment. With a bad alignment, you will not only have a bad time driving, but you will also
              ruin your tires. We do a complimentary check to see if you need an alignment. If so, our
              technicians will get your car going straight once again!
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
          <button class="btn btn-service danger-link btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseAcServices" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseAcServices">
            <div class="card-header text-center" id="headingAcServices">
              <h3 class="mb-0">
                A/C Services
              </h3>
            </div>
          </button>
          <div id="collapseAcServices" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingAcServices" data-parent="#servicesAccordion">
            <div class="card-body">
              Having an A/C unit that does not work in Texas can make any car feel like a furnace. Therefore,
              it is imperative that the A/C in your car works. However, if it does not work, our technicians can
              identify the problem and get your A/C blowing cold air once again!
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
          <button class="btn btn-service danger-link btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseBrakes" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseBrakes">
