                Brakes
              </h3>
            </div>
          </button>
          <div id="collapseBrakes" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingBrakes" data-parent="#servicesAccordion">
            <div class="card-body">
              The brakes on your car are one of the most important components that must work at all times.
              Without them, you run the risk of putting your life and your family’s life in danger. As a part of
              our complimentary inspection, we check not only your brake pads, but your rotors and brake
              fluid as well. If you are experiencing issues with your brakes, we are more than willing to help
              you out!
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
          <button class="btn btn-service danger-link btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseCheckEngineLight" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseCheckEngineLight">
